### List recent audit events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/audit/events?limit=50
X-Correlation-Id: local-list-audit-events

### List order audit events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/audit/events?aggregateType=ORDER&aggregateId={{orderId}}
X-Correlation-Id: local-order-audit-events

### List SKU audit events
GET http://localhost:8080/api/audit/events?aggregateType=SKU&aggregateId={{skuId}}
X-Correlation-Id: local-sku-audit-events
